{"type":"message","id":"0972332f","parentId":"878607b8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:00:30.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我具体是什么模型。根据系统信息，我看到：\n- model=zai/glm-5\n- default_model=zai/glm-5\n\n所以我运行的是 GLM-5 模型，通过 zai 提供商。我应该直接告诉他这个信息。\n\n模型别名中也提到：\n- GLM: zai/glm-5\n\n所以我就是 GLM-5。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我现在运行的是 **GLM-5**，通过 zai 提供商接入。\n\nGLM 是智谱 AI 的通用大语言模型系列。我现在的配置是 `zai/glm-5`。\n\n有什么想聊的或者需要帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7294,"output":214,"cacheRead":3136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774101621261}}
