{"type":"message","id":"d5e548d3","parentId":"3b50be86","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:09:50.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"里程计位置没有变化 (x: 0.8511, y: -0.4473)，说明小车可能没有真正移动，或者移动后又回到了原点。\n\n`front_distance: 2.033m` 还是很大，说明小车前方 2 米内没有障碍物。这很奇怪，如果小车在靠近蓝色水瓶，应该能看到障碍物才对。\n\n让我获取当前图像，看看水瓶的位置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_78b7c24299734a64a5078019","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TOOL=\"conda run -n mqtt-server python3 /home/userli/.openclaw/skills/ROS-limo-car/scripts/limo_ws_client.py\"\n\n$TOOL --host 172.31.94.183 --port 8765 get_image --camera-topic /usb_cam_0/image_raw --output /home/userli/.openclaw/workspace/limo_now.jpg","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2846,"output":277,"cacheRead":18496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21619,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774102180678}}
